Package com.gmail.aydinov.sergey.simple_debugger_plugin.abstraction

Interface TargetApplicationElementRepresentation

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
TargetApplicationClassOrInterfaceRepresentation
public interface TargetApplicationElementRepresentation extends Cloneable
Represents an element of the target application (class or interface) in the debugged JVM. Provides access to methods, fields, name, and type.

Author: Sergei Aidinov
Email: sergey.aydinov@gmail.com
